612
00:32:28,340 --> 00:32:30,540
I heard it from the Patrol Office.

613
00:32:31,980 --> 00:32:32,900
You know,

614
00:32:33,780 --> 00:32:35,580
I have a good relationship
with the Patrol Office.

615
00:32:36,140 --> 00:32:38,980
