no matter how serious it gets.

616
00:32:39,180 --> 00:32:40,620
Are you saying

617
00:32:41,700 --> 00:32:43,220
you can do whatever you want
and get away with it?

618
00:32:44,980 --> 00:32:45,460
No.

619
00:32:45,780 --> 00:32:46,780
What I mean is,

620
00:32:47,100 --> 00:32:48,820
