625
00:32:58,540 --> 00:33:01,020
People get targeted
not for who they are,

626
00:33:01,460 --> 00:33:02,940
but for what they have.

627
00:33:03,460 --> 00:33:05,380
If you were to run into robbers again,

628
00:33:05,940 --> 00:33:06,900
you could

629
00:33:07,700 --> 00:33:08,700
