630
00:33:08,900 --> 00:33:09,780
Ma Juncai,

631
00:33:11,540 --> 00:33:12,820
tell whoever you answer to

632
00:33:13,820 --> 00:33:15,860
that even if I lose my life,

633
00:33:15,860 --> 00:33:17,220
I will never yield.

634
00:33:17,580 --> 00:33:19,420
Should you reconsider

635
00:33:20,100 --> 00:33:22,380
our collaboration, Miss Chu,

636
00:33:23,220 --> 00:33:25,860
please do not hesitate to contact me.

637
00:33:35,860 --> 00:33:37,900
I tolerated seeing
you and Bai Bingxin together

638
00:33:39,300 --> 00:33:40,020
all the time.

639
00:33:41,420 --> 00:33:42,900
You made me throw all shame aside,

640
00:33:43,620 --> 00:33:44,580
create a scene,

641
00:33:45,380 --> 00:33:46,540
and drive her away.

642
00:33:49,340 --> 00:33:50,500
