654
00:34:19,340 --> 00:34:20,180
not even me.

655
00:34:23,100 --> 00:34:25,260
But you must trust money.

656
00:34:27,420 --> 00:34:28,460
The money I gave you

657
00:34:29,900 --> 00:34:32,340
