00:38:04,740 --> 00:38:05,740
I can't wait

698
00:38:05,740 --> 00:38:07,020
to go back to work.

699
00:38:07,020 --> 00:38:07,900
I've been going stir-crazy.

700
00:38:07,900 --> 00:38:08,540
Erniu,

701
00:38:08,980 --> 00:38:11,180
you can't go back yet.

702
00:38:12,060 --> 00:38:12,780
Why not?

703
00:38:13,220 --> 00:38:14,660
